OL,3,CHospital staff 'scared to come into
OL,4,Cwork' amid rising levels of patient
OL,5,Cviolence
OL,7,FHospital staff in Reading say they are
OL,8,Ffacing an alarming rise in violence
OL,9,Fand abuse from patients.
OL,11,FOne nurse at the Royal Berkshire
OL,12,FHospital, who has been both verbally
OL,13,Fand physically assaulted, told us the
OL,14,Fattacks left her terrified to go to
OL,15,Fwork.
OL,17,FThe trust says there were around 900
OL,18,Fcases reported by staff last year,
OL,19,Fwhich is why the hospital is now
OL,20,Fworking with Thames Valley Police.
