OL,5,Cviolence
OL,7,FThe scale, frequency and severity of
OL,8,Fthe abuse faced by the hospital's
OL,9,Fworkforce have been on the rise.
OL,11,FAttacks range from verbal threats to
OL,12,Fphysical violence including punching,
OL,13,Fkicking and spitting.
OL,15,FJess, an Emergency Department Sister
OL,16,Fat the Royal Berkshire Hospital said:
OL,17,F"We experience violence and aggression
OL,18,Ffrom patients at least on a daily
OL,19,Fbasis. From all different kinds of
OL,20,Fpatients.
