OL,3,CHospital staff 'scared to come into
OL,4,Cwork' amid rising levels of patient
OL,5,Cviolence
OL,7,F"It leaves you feeling scared to come
OL,8,Finto work.
OL,10,F"It's really frustrating because we're
OL,11,Fhere to help, not to be hurt.
OL,13,F"There's only so much we can do. We
OL,14,Fcome in to be nurses, doctors and
OL,15,Fhealthcare assistants to help people.
OL,17,F"That's the reason that we do the job
OL,18,Fand we don't deserve to be treated
OL,19,Fwith such violence and aggression."
