OL,3,CHospital staff 'scared to come into
OL,4,Cwork' amid rising levels of patient
OL,5,Cviolence
OL,7,FThe hospital is now working more
OL,8,Fclosely with Thames Valley Police as
OL,9,Fpart of a campaign called Operation
OL,10,FCavell.
OL,12,FEvery incident of assault against
OL,13,Fstaff will be reviewed by dedicated
OL,14,Finvestigators with an understanding of
OL,15,Fhealthcare environments to improve
OL,16,Fconviction rates and support victims.
