OL,7,FSteve McManus, Chief Executive of
OL,8,FRoyal Berkshire Hospital said: "We're
OL,9,Freally pleased that we're the first
OL,10,Forganisation in the NHS in the Thames
OL,11,FValley to adopt this.
OL,13,F"But what it also requires from us is
OL,14,Fto make sure that we're supporting
OL,15,Fstaff in having the time to work with
OL,16,Fthe police around reporting, providing
OL,17,Fthe information the data that they
OL,18,Fwill need to be able to make a
OL,19,Fjudgement about how they then address
OL,20,Fthat with a particular individual."
