OL,3,CHospital staff 'scared to come into
OL,4,Cwork' amid rising levels of patient
OL,5,Cviolence
OL,7,FDet Ch Supt Craig Kirby, Head of Crime
OL,8,Fand Intelligence at Thames Valley
OL,9,FPolice said: "These are people who
OL,10,Fhave been the victims of crime that
OL,11,Fare too often tolerating it.
OL,13,F"They're people that are working long
OL,14,Fhours whose sole purpose is to care
OL,15,Ffor us at a time of need and yet they
OL,16,Fare too often being subject to crimes
OL,17,Fand violence and aggression and that
OL,18,Fhas to stop.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
