OL,3,CHospital staff 'scared to come into
OL,4,Cwork' amid rising levels of patient
OL,5,Cviolence
OL,7,F"Hence Thames Valley Police is doing
OL,8,Feverything we can to ensure we deliver
OL,9,Fon that zero tolerance approach. "
OL,11,FCommenting on the initiative, Jess
OL,12,Fsaid: "I think it will be helpful and
OL,13,Fgive us some sense of security maybe,
OL,14,Fthat there is options there that can
OL,15,Fsupport us.
OL,17,F"We can't anticipate what's going to
OL,18,Fhappen but to know that we've got
OL,19,Fpeople that support us and help to
OL,20,Fprotect us, is really reassuring."
